msgstr "*Com a rede do host, a taxa de transferência do Quarkus melhora em 55%, enquanto o Spring se move em +2,3%.* Desativar o firewall na parte superior recupera outros 8% para o Quarkus, trazendo a proporção de 1,19x de volta para 1,97x - perto dos 2,08x do laboratório de desempenho."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Fedora's `firewalld` loads nearly 1000 https://wiki.nftables.org/[nftables] rules that every packet traverses. This is independent of pasta — disabling the firewall adds another 13% throughput in the pgbench test (18,106 → 20,402 TPS)."
msgstr "O `firewalld` do Fedora carrega quase 1.000 regras link:https://wiki.nftables.org/[do nftables] pelas quais cada pacote passa. Isso é independente da massa - a desativação do firewall adiciona mais 13% de taxa de transferência no teste do pgbench (18.106 → 20.402 TPS)."

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Why Quarkus is affected but Spring is not"
msgstr "Por que o Quarkus é afetado, mas o Spring não"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "As the pgbench data shows, pasta caps at ~18,000 TPS for a 2-query workload. pgbench is a minimal client that does nothing between queries — it represents the maximum throughput pasta can forward. Quarkus, which also processes HTTP requests, runs ORM and serialization between SQL queries, reaches 15,504 TPS through pasta — lower than pgbench's 18,106 because the application work between queries reduces the pressure on the proxy, but still constrained by it."
msgstr "Como mostram os dados do pgbench, o pasta atinge um limite de aproximadamente 18.000 TPS para uma carga de trabalho de duas consultas. O pgbench é um cliente mínimo que não faz nada entre as consultas - ele representa a taxa de transferência máxima que o pasta pode encaminhar. O Quarkus, que também processa solicitações HTTP, executa ORM e serialização entre as consultas SQL, atinge 15.504 TPS por meio do pasta - menos do que os 18.106 do pgbench porque o trabalho do aplicativo entre as consultas reduz a pressão sobre o proxy, mas ainda é limitado por ele."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "With host networking, Quarkus reaches ~24,000 TPS — well above what pasta can deliver. Spring reaches ~13,000 TPS, which is below pasta's ceiling regardless of networking mode. **Any application that can push close to pasta's ceiling will be constrained by it; any application that stays well below it will not notice.**"
msgstr "Com a rede de host, o Quarkus alcança cerca de 24.000 TPS, bem acima do que o pasta pode oferecer. O Spring atinge cerca de 13.000 TPS, o que está abaixo do teto do pasta, independentemente do modo de rede. *Qualquer aplicativo que consiga chegar perto do teto do pasta será limitado por ele; qualquer aplicativo que fique bem abaixo dele não perceberá.*"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Confirming the fix"
msgstr "Confirmação da correção"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A second differential flamegraph — this time comparing the local default (pasta) run with the local `--network=host` run — confirms the overhead is gone:"
msgstr "Um segundo gráfico de chama diferencial, desta vez comparando a execução padrão local (pasta) com a execução local `--network=host` , confirma que a sobrecarga desapareceu:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Red means more CPU in the default (pasta) run; blue means more CPU with host networking. The red stacks that dominated the first flamegraph — `_raw_spin_unlock_irqrestore`, `nft_do_chain`, `tcp_clean_rtx_queue` — have disappeared."
msgstr "Vermelho significa mais CPU na execução padrão (pasta); azul significa mais CPU com rede de host. As pilhas vermelhas que dominaram o primeiro gráfico de chama - `_raw_spin_unlock_irqrestore` , `nft_do_chain` , `tcp_clean_rtx_queue` - desapareceram."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**With `--network=host`, the app and PostgreSQL share the same network namespace; packets never leave the kernel.**"
msgstr "*Com --network=host, o aplicativo e o PostgreSQL compartilham o mesmo namespace de rede; os pacotes nunca deixam o kernel.*"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Takeaways"
msgstr "Conclusões"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**A benchmark that saturates an unexpected resource and component is not measuring what you think.** This is what Brendan Gregg calls https://www.brendangregg.com/activebenchmarking.html[active benchmarking]:"
msgstr "*Um benchmark que satura um recurso e um componente inesperados não está medindo o que o senhor pensa.* Isso é o que Brendan Gregg chama de link:https://www.brendangregg.com/activebenchmarking.html[benchmarking ativo] :"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "_You benchmark A, but actually measure B, and conclude you've measured C._"
msgstr "_O senhor faz o benchmark de A, mas na verdade mede B e conclui que mediu C._"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We benchmarked framework throughput, but Quarkus was saturating pasta's single CPU core — so we were measuring pasta's forwarding capacity, not framework performance. Only by collecting https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man1/mpstat.1.html[mpstat] and flamegraphs _during_ the run — as https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/issues/62[required by our benchmarking practice] — did we identify which resource and component was saturated. Without that, the 1.19x ratio would have been taken at face value."
msgstr "Fizemos um benchmarking do rendimento da estrutura, mas o Quarkus estava saturando o núcleo único da CPU do Pasta - portanto, estávamos medindo a capacidade de encaminhamento do Pasta, não o desempenho da estrutura. Somente coletando link:https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man1/mpstat.1.html[mpstat] e flamegraphs _durante a_ execução - conforme link:https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/issues/62[exigido pela nossa prática de benchmarking] - identificamos qual recurso e componente estava saturado. Sem isso, a proporção de 1,19x teria sido considerada como valor nominal."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**The impact is asymmetric.** Pasta's single-threaded ceiling affects only applications whose throughput would otherwise exceed it. In this benchmark, Quarkus exceeds the ceiling and is capped; Spring does not and is unaffected. The same logic applies to any workload — the proxy is invisible until you hit its limit."
msgstr "*O impacto é assimétrico.* O limite máximo de thread único do Pasta afeta apenas os aplicativos cuja taxa de transferência o excederia. Nesse benchmark, o Quarkus excede o teto e é limitado; o Spring não excede e não é afetado. A mesma lógica se aplica a qualquer carga de trabalho - o proxy é invisível até que o usuário atinja o limite."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Check your networking path.** Run `podman info | grep rootlessNetworkCmd` to see your backend. If it says `pasta` and your benchmark talks to a containerized database, use `--network=host` for the database container."
msgstr "*Verifique seu caminho de rede.* Execute `podman info | grep rootlessNetworkCmd` para ver seu backend. Se ele indicar `pasta` e seu benchmark se comunicar com um banco de dados em contêiner, use `--network=host` para o contêiner do banco de dados."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Firewall rules add up.** Nearly 1000 nftables rules cost 8-13% throughput on this workload (8% for Quarkus with host networking, 13% for pgbench through pasta). For benchmarking, consider temporarily disabling the firewall or using a minimal ruleset."
msgstr "*As regras de firewall aumentam.* Cerca de 1.000 regras do nftables custam de 8% a 13% da taxa de transferência nessa carga de trabalho (8% para o Quarkus com rede de host, 13% para o pgbench por meio de pasta). Para o benchmarking, considere desativar temporariamente o firewall ou usar um conjunto mínimo de regras."

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Known upstream issues"
msgstr "Problemas conhecidos de upstream"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Our findings are consistent with several known issues in the podman/pasta ecosystem:"
msgstr "Nossas descobertas são consistentes com vários problemas conhecidos no ecossistema podman/pasta:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**pasta is single-threaded by design** and degrades under concurrent load. Community reports confirm that above ~8 connections, even the older https://github.com/rootless-containers/slirp4netns[slirp4netns] backend can outperform it. (https://github.com/containers/podman/discussions/22559[Podman Discussion #22559])"
msgstr "*O pasta é de thread único por padrão* e se degrada sob carga simultânea. Os relatórios da comunidade confirmam que, acima de aproximadamente 8 conexões, até mesmo o backend mais antigo link:https://github.com/rootless-containers/slirp4netns[do slirp4netns] pode superá-lo. ( link:https://github.com/containers/podman/discussions/22559[Podman Discussion #22559] )"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**pasta consuming 90-100% CPU** has been reported under sustained network load, e.g. Wireguard tunnels on kernel 6.x. (https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/23686[Podman Issue #23686])"
msgstr "Foi relatado que *a massa que consome 90-100% da CPU* sob carga de rede sustentada, por exemplo, túneis Wireguard no kernel 6.x. ( link:https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/23686[Podman Issue #23686] )"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Java + PostgreSQL hang** -- a Spring app running PostgreSQL `COPY FROM STDIN` via pasta consistently freezes mid-transfer. `--network=host` fixes it. (https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/22593[Podman Issue #22593])"
msgstr "*Java + PostgreSQL travado* - um aplicativo Spring que executa o PostgreSQL `COPY FROM STDIN` via pasta congela consistentemente no meio da transferência. `--network=host` corrige o problema. ( link:https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/22593[Problema #22593 do Podman] )"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Throughput far below host capacity** -- rootless containers on multi-gigabit hosts achieving only ~100 Mbit/s through pasta. (https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/17865[Podman Issue #17865])"
msgstr "*Taxa de transferência muito abaixo da capacidade do host* - contêineres sem raiz em hosts multigigabit atingem apenas ~100 Mbit/s por meio de pasta. ( link:https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/17865[Problema Podman nº 17865] )"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Traffic stalls under sustained load** -- TCP downloads through pasta start normally then halt, with pasta pinned at high CPU. (https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/17703[Podman Issue #17703])"
msgstr "*O tráfego é interrompido sob carga contínua* - os downloads TCP através do pasta começam normalmente e depois param, com o pasta preso em uma CPU alta. ( link:https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/17703[Problema nº 17703 do Podman] )"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-08-hidden-cost-rootless-container-networking.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The official https://github.com/containers/podman/blob/main/docs/tutorials/performance.md[Podman performance tutorial] documents `--network=host` and socket activation as workarounds for network-sensitive workloads."
msgstr "O link:https://github.com/containers/podman/blob/main/docs/tutorials/performance.md[tutorial] oficial link:https://github.com/containers/podman/blob/main/docs/tutorials/performance.md[de desempenho do Podman] documenta `--network=host` e ativação de soquete como soluções alternativas para cargas de trabalho sensíveis à rede."
